    "title": "Hiring Store Manager at Metro Cash & Carry Capital India",
    "description": "Metro Cash & Carry Capital India invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Store Manager at our Pune location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Metro Cash & Carry Capital India:\nMetro Cash & Carry Capital India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pune, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Metro Cash & Carry Capital India!",
